{
  "page": "Smoking Log",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Smoking_Log_(AGoT_Comic).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/Smoking_Log_%28AGoT_Comic%29.jpg/300px-Smoking_Log_%28AGoT_Comic%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"280\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/Smoking_Log_%28AGoT_Comic%29.jpg/450px-Smoking_Log_%28AGoT_Comic%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/a/a8/Smoking_Log_%28AGoT_Comic%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Smoking_Log_(AGoT_Comic).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Theon, Bran, and Robb encounter Kyra outside the Smoking Log by Tommy Patterson for <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)\" title=\"A Game of Thrones (comics)\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> comic</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Smoking Log</b> is an inn and <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">alehouse</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Winter_town\" title=\"Winter town\">winter town</a> outside of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smoking_Log&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smoking_Log&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> pass through the <a href=\"/index.php/Winter_town\" title=\"Winter town\">winter town</a> on Bran's first ride since his fall, they pass by the Smoking Log. They encounter <a href=\"/index.php/Kyra\" title=\"Kyra\">Kyra</a> and another girl standing by the sign outide the inn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>A <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">Bolton</a> man stabs a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cerwyn\" title=\"House Cerwyn\">Cerwyn</a> man in the Smoking Log after <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> calls his banners.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smoking_Log&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3